        Clarity and Diction
        ${courseContent['Voice-Over Basics']['To excel in voice-over work, consider these fundamental principles']['Clarity and Diction']}
        
        Tone and Emotion
        ${courseContent['Voice-Over Basics']['To excel in voice-over work, consider these fundamental principles']['Tone and Emotion']}

        Timing and Pacing
        ${courseContent['Voice-Over Basics']['To excel in voice-over work, consider these fundamental principles']['Timing and Pacing']}

        Script Interpretation
        ${courseContent['Voice-Over Basics']['To excel in voice-over work, consider these fundamental principles']['Script Interpretation']}

Have fun! If you get stuck, we will be happy to help at Storyshell.io
`;

